# guessing_game

A small command-line "guess the number" game written in Rust. This is from the book **"The The Rust Programming Language"**
*by Steve Klabnik, Carol Nichols, and Chris Krycho, with contributions from the Rust Community*.

## Features
- Simple CLI gameplay: guess a randomly generated number
- Built with Cargo
- Minimal, easy-to-read source for learning

## Requirements
- Rust and Cargo (https://rustup.rs)

## Build & Run
Build in debug:
```bash
cargo build
```